data.description: Stunning Modern Farmhouse renovation you won't want to miss! Looks like an HGTV home, this charmer has been completely transformed and is ready for its new family! Spacious main floor living area with a completely new kitchen with new stainless steel appliances, new cabinets, and countertops, large bedroom with an updated bath including new shower, toilet, and vanity. Stunning new craftsman style staircase leading you to an open and roomy upper level where you will find three bedrooms; master has a walk-in closet, bath with new vanity, double sinks, shower, and toilet. There’s yet another renovated bath, complete with vanity, toilet, and shower, and a second-floor laundry room complete with stainless steel full-size stackable washer and dryer. Your choice...master bedroom upstairs or on the main level. New siding, New Hot water heater, newer windows, A/C & Heat. Set up a showing today!
